<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Importance of Entrepreneurship - Seminar</title>
    <style>
        /* --- Reset & Global Styles --- */
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            background: #0f172a;
            color: #f8fafc;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        /* --- Smooth Scroll Container --- */
        scroll-container {
            display: block;
            height: 100vh;
            overflow-y: scroll;
            scroll-snap-type: y mandatory;
        }

        /* --- Slide Section Design --- */
        .slide {
            height: 100vh;
            width: 100vw;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 2rem;
            position: relative;
            scroll-snap-align: start;
            background: radial-gradient(circle at center, #1e293b 0%, #0f172a 100%);
        }

        /* --- Scroll Progress Bar --- */
        .progress-bar {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            height: 5px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #38bdf8, #818cf8);
            width: 0%;
            z-index: 100;
            transition: width 0.1s ease-out;
        }

        /* --- Typography & Layout --- */
        h1 {
            font-size: 3.5rem;
            color: #38bdf8;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            text-align: center;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
        }

        h2 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            color: #818cf8;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #334155;
            padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            line-height: 1.8;
            max-width: 800px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #cbd5e1;
        }

        .highlight {
            color: #38bdf8;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        /* Grid for Points */
        .grid-container {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
            gap: 1.5rem;
            max-width: 1200px;
            width: 100%;
            margin-top: 1rem;
        }

        .card {
            background: rgba(30, 41, 59, 0.7);
            border: 1px solid #334155;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, border-color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            border-color: #38bdf8;
        }

        .card h3 {
            color: #38bdf8;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
        }

        .card p {
            font-size: 1rem;
            text-align: left;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        /* --- Animation Engine (Classes toggled by JS) --- */
        .reveal {
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateY(40px);
            transition: all 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.25, 1, 0.5, 1);
        }

        .reveal.active {
            opacity: 1;
            transform: translateY(0);
        }

        /* Staggered entry for cards */
        .card {
            opacity: 0;
            transform: scale(0.9);
            transition: opacity 0.6s ease, transform 0.6s ease, border-color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .reveal.active .card {
            opacity: 1;
            transform: scale(1);
        }

        /* Adding delay for cards */
        .reveal.active .card:nth-child(1) { transition-delay: 0.1s; }
        .reveal.active .card:nth-child(2) { transition-delay: 0.2s; }
        .reveal.active .card:nth-child(3) { transition-delay: 0.3s; }
        .reveal.active .card:nth-child(4) { transition-delay: 0.4s; }
        .reveal.active .card:nth-child(5) { transition-delay: 0.5s; }
        .reveal.active .card:nth-child(6) { transition-delay: 0.6s; }
        .reveal.active .card:nth-child(7) { transition-delay: 0.7s; }

        /* Navigation Tips */
        .scroll-hint {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 2rem;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #64748b;
            animation: bounce 2s infinite;
        }

        @keyframes bounce {
            0%, 20%, 50%, 80%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); }
            40% { transform: translateY(-10px); }
            60% { transform: translateY(-5px); }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="progress-bar" id="progressBar"></div>

    <scroll-container id="scrollContainer">
        
        <section class="slide reveal">
            <h1>Importance of<br><span style="color: #818cf8;">Entrepreneurship</span></h1>
            <p style="font-size: 1.5rem; color: #94a3b8;">A Seminar Presentation</p>
            <div class="scroll-hint">↓ Scroll down to begin</div>
        </section>

        <section class="slide reveal">
            <h2>Introduction</h2>
            <p>Good morning everyone. Today I am going to present a seminar on <strong>"Importance of Entrepreneurship."</strong></p>
            <br>
            <p>Entrepreneurship is one of the key factors for economic and social development. Entrepreneurs create new businesses, generate employment, and introduce innovative ideas. They contribute significantly to the growth of a nation.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="slide reveal">
            <h2>Definition</h2>
            <p style="font-size: 1.8rem; line-height: 1.6; max-width: 900px;">
                "Entrepreneurship is the process of <span class="highlight">identifying opportunities</span>, 
                <span class="highlight">taking risks</span>, organizing resources, and starting a business 
                to earn profit and provide value to society."
            </p>
        </section>

        <section class="slide reveal">
            <h2>Why Entrepreneurship Matters</h2>
            <div class="grid-container">
                <div class="card">
                    <h3>1. Creates Employment</h3>
                    <p>Entrepreneurs establish new businesses and industries, creating jobs for many people and reducing unemployment.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="card">
                    <h3>2. Promotes Innovation</h3>
                    <p>Entrepreneurs introduce new products, services, and technologies that improve people's lives and solve problems.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="card">
                    <h3>3. Supports Economic Growth</h3>
                    <p>Entrepreneurship increases production, income, and investment, contributing to the growth of the country's economy.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="card">
                    <h3>4. Improves Living Standards</h3>
                    <p>New products and services improve the quality of life and provide better choices for consumers.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="slide reveal">
            <h2>Driving Development</h2>
            <div class="grid-container" style="grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(320px, 1fr)); max-width: 1000px;">
                <div class="card">
                    <h3>5. Encourages Self-Reliance</h3>
                    <p>Entrepreneurship helps individuals become independent by creating their own employment instead of depending on others for jobs.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="card">
                    <h3>6. Utilizes Resources Effectively</h3>
                    <p>Entrepreneurs make efficient use of available resources such as labor, capital, and technology.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="card">
                    <h3>7. Promotes Regional Development</h3>
                    <p>Businesses established in rural and underdeveloped areas help improve infrastructure and create local employment.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="slide reveal">
            <h2>Conclusion</h2>
            <p>In conclusion, entrepreneurship plays a vital role in economic and social development. It creates employment, promotes innovation, improves living standards, and contributes to national growth.</p>
            <br>
            <p style="color: #38bdf8; font-weight: bold;">Therefore, entrepreneurship is essential for building a prosperous and self-reliant society.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="slide reveal">
            <h1 style="font-size: 5rem; background: linear-gradient(45deg, #38bdf8, #818cf8); -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;">Thank You</h1>
            <p>Questions & Answers</p>
        </section>

    </scroll-container>

    <script>
        const container = document.getElementById('scrollContainer');
        const progressBar = document.getElementById('progressBar');
        const slides = document.querySelectorAll('.reveal');

        // 1. Update Progress Bar on Scroll
        container.addEventListener('scroll', () => {
            const maxScroll = container.scrollHeight - container.clientHeight;
            const percentage = (container.scrollTop / maxScroll) * 100;
            progressBar.style.width = percentage + '%';
        });

        // 2. Intersection Observer to Trigger Slide Animations
        const observerOptions = {
            root: container,
            threshold: 0.4 // Triggers when 40% of the slide is visible
        };

        const slideObserver = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {
            entries.forEach(entry => {
                if (entry.isIntersecting) {
                    entry.target.classList.add('active');
                } else {
                    // Optional: Remove class to re-animate when scrolling back up
                    entry.target.classList.remove('active'); 
                }
            });
        }, observerOptions);

        slides.forEach(slide => slideObserver.observe(slide));

        // Activate the first slide instantly on load
        window.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
            if(slides.length > 0) slides[0].classList.add('active');
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>
